Friday, October 27, 2000

RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

00-1640. State ex rel. Ohio Heritage Dev. Co. v. Portage Cty. Bd. of Elections.

In Prohibition. Reported at 90 Ohio St.3d 1436, 736 N.E.2d 476. IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration in this case be, and hereby is, denied.
